title: 12/01/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 12/01/21 DPS Best Of
description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP talks to new LSU Head Coach Brian Kelly about his decision to leave South Bend for Baton Rouge. When did he make the decision? CBS CFB Analyst Rick Neuheisel calls in to discuss the College Football landscape and who he thinks will get the Notre Dame vacancy. And Matt Leinart weighs in on USC's hiring of Lincoln Riley, as well as DP's disdain for FireBall Whiskey
